# TRMNL Design System

When generating templaes for a plugin 
- use the styles in [plugins.css](mdc:design-system/cdn-copy-20250201/plugins.css) where possible since these are use by the real TRMNL server for rendering.
- examples in @description.example.html @label.example.html @table.example.html @title-bar.example.html @title.example.html @title-bar.example.html @clamp.example.html may help

- do not include the header tags in a plugin, just include any styles in the body however just use those in [styles.css](mdc:design-system/styles.css) where possible based on the above examples

- secrets should not go into the plugin.json file. add these to the .env as additional_query_string_params

Always put the title_bar at the bottom of page